Metadata: Headwaters (Volume 2, Issue 4, December 2015): Publication of Maryland Sea Grant Extension Watershed Educators
University of Maryland Sea Grant Extension Program
Four newsletter issues in 2015 (MDU-N-15-06a; MDU-N-15-06b; MDU-N-15-06c; MDU-N-15-06d)

Headwaters is a publication of Maryland Sea Grant Extension Watershed Educators. Inside this issue are the following topics: +Slowing the flow at Oregon Ridge; + Hot on the streets-the Outreach Program audit tool; +Seeking tall, attractive native grass to help with bay clean-up; +Restoring the American chestnut; + Risk perceptions in vulnerable communities.
